@gunan Looks like one_hot_op_test.py and trace_op_test.py succeeded, but diag_op_test.py failed for mysterious reasons. 2 out of 3 isn't bad:

http://ci.tensorflow.org/job/tf-pr-win-cmake-gpu/10/console

I re-disabled diag_op_test.py for the time being. Shall we merge this, since it should at least prevent ugly crashes?
